---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="首页"
  description="集成式自我探索平台——大五人格、哲学气质、核心价值观、依恋风格等17大科学测评，全方位了解你自己。"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-700 to-primary-900 text-white">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
          探索<span class="text-yellow-300">完整的</span>自己
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          17大科学测评，从人格、哲学、价值观、情商、金钱观到气质、边界、内耗，全方位深度认识你自己。
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary-200">全部免费 · 无需注册 · 数据保留在本地浏览器</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Classic Scientific Tests -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-2">📋 经典科学测评</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-10 text-sm">基于国际公认心理学量表，科学、严谨、深度</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Big Five Full -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}quiz`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🧠</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">最全面</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">大五人格 · 完整版</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">IPIP-NEO-120 国际权威量表</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">140题 · 15-20分钟 · 5大维度 + 30子维度深度拆解、雷达图、职场/人际/抗压分析、足球位置匹配</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Big Five Short -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}short`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 text-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">⚡</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-green-50 text-green-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">快速版</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">大五人格 · 简洁版</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">IPIP-50 简版量表</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">50题 · 5-8分钟 · 快速勾勒五大维度人格轮廓、雷达图、百分位排名</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Philosophy -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}philosophy`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🏛️</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">特色</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">哲学气质测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">18个东西方哲学流派</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">60题 · 8-10分钟 · 尼采、孔子、萨特、庄子…探索你的哲学DNA与思想气质</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Values -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}values`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">💎</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">指南针</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">核心价值观测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Schwartz 10种基本价值观</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">40题 · 约5分钟 · 基于生活场景，了解驱动你人生选择的核心价值</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Attachment -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}attachment`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 text-pink-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">💕</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-pink-50 text-pink-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">关系</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">爱情依恋风格测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">成人依恋理论 ECR</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">36题 · 4-5分钟 · 安全型/焦虑型/回避型/恐惧型——了解你的亲密关系模式</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-pink-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- EQ -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}eq`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 text-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🧠</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">情绪</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">情商EQ测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Goleman 情商模型</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">25题 · 3-5分钟 · 自我觉察、情绪管理、同理心、社交技巧、自我激励五维度分析</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fun & Practical Tests -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-2">🎯 趣味实用测评</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-10 text-sm">有趣又富有洞察力，发现你生活中的另一面</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Temperament -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}temperament`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 text-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🍵</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">热点</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">淡人/浓人气质鉴定</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">情绪唤醒与反应性模型</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">20题 · 2-3分钟 · 你是心如止水的"古希腊掌管淡定的神"，还是热烈抓马的"浓缩火药桶"？</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Boundary -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}boundary`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🦔</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-rose-50 text-rose-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">人际</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">讨好型/不好惹指数</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">社交边界与坚定性评估</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">25题 · 3分钟 · 你是习惯性委屈自己的"便利贴"，还是自带结界的"带刺玫瑰"？</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-rose-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Meritocracy -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}meritocracy`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🏆</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">价值观</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">优绩主义程度测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">6维度成功观分析</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">24题 · 3-4分钟 · 你对"努力=成功"有多相信？内卷还是躺平？</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Overthinking -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}overthinking`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-violet-100 text-violet-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🌀</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-violet-50 text-violet-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">认知</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">精神内耗指数测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">5维度认知消耗分析</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">20题 · 2-3分钟 · 你是"内耗永动机"还是"人间清醒"？测测你的心理带宽消耗。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-violet-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Procrastination -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}procrastination`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">⏳</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">行为</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">拖延症类型鉴定</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">5维度执行功能分析</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">20题 · 2-3分钟 · 你是"死线战神"还是"完美主义瘫痪"？找到你拖延的根源。</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-cyan-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Spirit Animal -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}animal`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🦁</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">趣味</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">性格动物匹配</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">8种动物原型</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">30题 · 3-5分钟 · 狮子、猫头鹰、海豚、狐狸…找到代表你性格的精神动物</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Decision Style -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}decision`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">🧭</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">成长</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">决策风格测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">4种决策模式</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">30题 · 3-5分钟 · 分析型、直觉型、集思广益型、审慎型——你是哪种决策者？</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-indigo-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Social Style -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}social`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">💬</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">人际</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">社交风格测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">4种沟通风格</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">30题 · 3-5分钟 · 驱动型、表达型、亲和型、分析型——你的沟通DNA是什么？</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Stress Coping -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}stress`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">💪</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-red-50 text-red-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">健康</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">压力应对方式测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">4种应对模式</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">24题 · 2-3分钟 · 了解你面对压力时的真实反应模式，学会更健康地应对</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Money Mindset -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}money`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">💰</div>
            <span class="text-xs bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">财富</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">金钱观念测评</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">5种金钱人格</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">20题 · 2-3分钟 · 储蓄家、享受派、投资者、极简者、分享者——你的金钱DNA</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">开始测评 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>

        <!-- Methods -->
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}methods`} class="card group hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 block bg-gray-50 border-dashed">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">📖</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">测评方法论</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">了解科学依据</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">所有11个测评的理论基础、量表来源、信效度数据与隐私承诺</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 font-medium text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">了解更多 <span>→</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OCEAN Overview (compact) -->
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4">大五人格模型（OCEAN）</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm">
        大五人格是目前心理学界最广泛接受的人格结构模型，以下五个维度是理解人格的基础。
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
        <div class="card text-center border-t-4 border-red-500 py-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#e74c3c">开放性 O</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">好奇心与想象力</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center border-t-4 border-blue-500 py-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📋</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#3498db">尽责性 C</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">自律与条理</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center border-t-4 border-orange-400 py-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎉</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#f39c12">外向性 E</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">社交与活力</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center border-t-4 border-green-500 py-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#2ecc71">宜人性 A</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">合作与同情</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center border-t-4 border-purple-500 py-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🧘</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#9b59b6">神经质 N</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">情绪稳定性</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 py-10 text-center text-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-2">
        <p>本平台所有测评仅供个人了解与参考，不构成临床诊断</p>
        <p>所有数据完全存储在您的浏览器本地，我们不会收集、上传或存储您的任何答题数据</p>
        <p>
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}methods`} class="hover:text-white underline underline-offset-2">测评方法论</a>
          <span class="mx-3">·</span>
          <span>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} 自我探索平台</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
